Carnage/Teltoli

* Carnage lay on the ground breathing hard, she watched Rage enter the 
forest and disappear into it's depths and thanked the Matrix that she was 
still alive.
A wash of cool wind swept over her as Teltoli broke wind with her wings and 
landed beside her, she had wondered where the Fuzor had been.*

Carnage: "Where were you?!"

* Teltoli looked at Carnage in a confused way.*

Teltoli: " I was looking for you. One minuet you're trailing behind me the 
next there's no sign of you. What happened?"

* Carnage sighed as she got to her feet and shook her body, obviously the 
fall wasn't that pleasant!*

Carnage: " Some jack-ass raptor jumped me from the side and tried to attack 
me, then when I attacked back it began to scream all these things like, 'Get 
out' and 'You're on my land' sort of stuff."
*Carnage snarled, she could still remember the smell of the clone and the 
way it spoke. It sent a shiver down her spine, it was SO MUCH like Dinobot 
that if it hadn't been a female Carnage would have been sure that it was 
him.*

* Teltoli cocked her head to one side and raised her ears.*
Teltoli: " Was it a bot, a Maximal?"

*Carnage bared her teeth.*
Carnage: " It is a bot but I doubt very much if it was a Maximal.It was to 
harsh then suddenly to cowardly. You know, when I attacked it back the only 
thing that it did was yell at me. That's it, yell at me."

*Teltoli sighed, again they had had contact with another bot and again it 
had to be spoiled by....*
Teltoli: " Carnage? What made the other bot leave?"

*Carnage looked at and flexed her figures, it had been hard swinging from 
Rage's jaw like that and she didn't care to do it again!*
Carnage: " Some Tarbosarus burst from the forest and grabbed the other 
raptor, it was beginning to eat it like it was some sort of tasty treat or 
somethin. Of course, I had to save the damn thing and when I did the jerk 
flew off without a word of thanx!
Last time I ever do it a favor!"
